Rise - Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy for Rise Habit Tracker App
At Rise Habit Tracker, we take user privacy and data protection seriously. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle and safeguard user data within our app.
Collection of Data:
Rise Habit Tracker does not collect or store any personal or sensitive user data.
All habit tracking data entered by the user remains stored only on the user's local device storage.
Usage of Data:
The habit tracking data stored locally on the user's device is solely for the purpose of providing the intended functionality of the app.
We do not access, use, or share any user data for any other purposes.
Data Security:
We have implemented appropriate technical and organizational measures to ensure the security and protection of user data.
All habit tracking data is stored locally on the user's device and is not transmitted or synced with any external servers.
Third-Party Services:
Rise Habit Tracker does not integrate or use any third-party services that may collect or access user data.
Contact Information:
If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding your privacy or data security, you can contact us at
thinklikepro@gmail.com
.
Children's Privacy:
Rise Habit Tracker is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13.
We do not knowingly collect any personal information from children.
Changes to Privacy Policy:
We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time.
Any changes to the Privacy Policy will be reflected within the app or on our website.
By using Rise Habit Tracker, you acknowledge and agree to the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy.
